This super sweet locket has plenty of room for your favourite photos or memories! It features a small glass dome connector, in your choice of red, blue, turquoise or yellow floral, with a tiny dove charm. 

The locket measures 3.5cm x 1.5cm, with enough room for four photos or messages measuring 1.3cm x 2.4cm. It hangs from a 70cm antiqued brass cable chain.

Please note that this piece is made-to-order - you will need to allow up to seven days from the date of purchase for it to be crafted.
